{
  "page": "Saffron",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">This article is about the daughter of a <a href=\"/index.php/Gulltown\" title=\"Gulltown\">Gulltown</a> merchant. For the <a href=\"/index.php/Spice\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Spice\">spice</a>, see <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saffron\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Saffron\">Saffron</a>. For the strait, see <a href=\"/index.php/Saffron_Straits\" title=\"Saffron Straits\">Saffron Straits</a>.</div>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Saffron</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valemen\" title=\"Valemen\">Valemen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Lover</th><td>\nSer <a href=\"/index.php/Harrold_Hardyng\" title=\"Harrold Hardyng\">Harrold Hardyng</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\nUnborn bastard<sup id=\"cite_ref-twow_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-twow-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Saffron</b> is the daughter of a spice merchant from <a href=\"/index.php/Gulltown\" title=\"Gulltown\">Gulltown</a>, the richest man in the city.<sup id=\"cite_ref-twow_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-twow-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Saffron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Saffron is described as tall and slim, with big brown eyes and hair like honey. Her father considers her more precious than gold.<sup id=\"cite_ref-twow_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-twow-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Saffron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Saffron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a>, who is masquerading as <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> daughter, \"Alayne Stone\", hears gossip from <a href=\"/index.php/Myranda_Royce\" title=\"Myranda Royce\">Myranda Royce</a> that, despite his youth, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harrold_Hardyng\" title=\"Harrold Hardyng\">Harrold Hardyng</a> has already fathered at least one baseborn child, with another on the way. Later, Petyr tells Alayne that he has arranged to betroth her to Harrold.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Saffron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>At the <a href=\"/index.php/Gates_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Gates of the Moon\">Gates of the Moon</a>, during the feast for the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> for the <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_of_Winged_Knights\" title=\"Brotherhood of Winged Knights\">Brotherhood of Winged Knights</a>, Alayne dances with Harrold, and inquires about his bastards, to which he answers in all honesty. He tells her of his two-year-old daughter <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Stone\" title=\"Alys Stone\">Alys Stone</a>, fathered on a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Waynwood\" title=\"House Waynwood\">House Waynwood</a> servant, <a href=\"/index.php/Cissy\" title=\"Cissy\">Cissy</a>. According to Harrold, childbirth left Cissy \"fat as a cow\", so Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Anya_Waynwood\" title=\"Anya Waynwood\">Anya Waynwood</a> arranged for her to be married off to one of her <a href=\"/index.php/Men-at-arms\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Men-at-arms\">men-at-arms</a>. However, Harrold says it is different with Saffron, who he has impregnated with his second child. Alayne is amused by Saffron's name, and Harrold explains that her father is a spice merchant in <a href=\"/index.php/Gulltown\" title=\"Gulltown\">Gulltown</a>, the richest man in the city, who considers his daughter more precious than gold. Alayne jokingly asks Harrold if he plans to name the child \"Cinnamon\" if it's a girl, or \"Cloves\" if it's a boy. Harrold is impressed with Alayne's cleverness, and Alayne tells him if they marry, he will have to send Saffron back to her father.<sup id=\"cite_ref-twow_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-twow-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Saffron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Harrold</b>: It is different with Saffron.<br /><b>Alayne</b>: Saffron? Truly?<br /><b>Harrold</b>: Her father says she is more precious to him than gold.<sup id=\"cite_ref-twow_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-twow-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Harrold_Hardyng\" title=\"Harrold Hardyng\">Harrold Hardyng</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Alayne_Stone\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Alayne Stone\">Alayne Stone</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Should we ever wed, you'll have to send Saffron back to her father. I'll be all the spice you'll want.<sup id=\"cite_ref-twow_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-twow-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Alayne_Stone\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Alayne Stone\">Alayne Stone</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Harrold_Hardyng\" title=\"Harrold Hardyng\">Harrold Hardyng</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Saffron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-twow-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-twow_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-twow_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-twow_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-twow_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-twow_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-twow_1-5\">1.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Alayne_I_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Alayne I (The Winds of Winter)\">Alayne I</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_41\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 41\">Chapter 41</a>, Alayne II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404061830\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.079 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.268 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 551/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10990/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7544/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1290/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1537/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.92 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  252.767      1 -total\n 79.93%  202.025      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 79.14%  200.050      1 Template:Infobox\n 15.76%   39.833      1 Template:About\n 11.04%   27.894     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.57%    9.029      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.59%    4.028      1 Template:Ref\n  1.17%    2.954      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.82%    2.060      2 Template:Warning/twow\n  0.77%    1.937      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:21037-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404061829 and revision id 296147\n -->\n",
